title: Unable to see Match history details
body:
Since the update, after I click into a match history I can't see any other tabs such as overview, stats, graphs and runes. 
Is anyone experiencing the same?

replies.body:
No issues on mine. So when you select a game from match history the tabs just aren't there?

Try running a **client repair** through settings (the gear icon top right) > Initiate Full Repair.
tabs are there but when I click it nothing comes on the screen.

If you don't have any luck with the repair you might have to reinstall, but you can submit a ticket to player support and they might be able to help you more: https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new
